    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Objects that can function both as muffs and as receptacles for personal items. Often these are designed as handbags with an opening in the back in which the hands can be inserted, or conversely, muffs with an appended pouch.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
